(1, 250, 'Hugo Magalhães', 'hugomn@gmail.com', '', '186.249.1.106', '2014-09-02 12:57:00', '2014-09-02 12:57:00', 'Nice article, Tiago! Really clear and focusing in what, for me, is the next (oy maybe the actual) generation of the web flow. I just have an additional point: I really think that a new rising area we have now is the RESTFull APIs development. This is a really great area for software developers that still want to develop backend experiences. I feel a lack of good professionals in this area. Thanks a lot for sharing your knowledge! Regards. ;)', 0, '1', 'Disqus/1.1(2.84):1570153805', '', 0, 0),
(2, 166, 'Alex Miranda', 'alexmirandamoraes@gmail.com', 'http://alexmiranda.net', '187.49.237.214', '2014-09-03 13:40:00', '2014-09-03 13:40:00', 'Hi Elaine,\nNice post! That''s true, for most of us working with Agile methodologies they''ve really become every day words, and sometimes we don''t even need to make the connection with their original meaning to explain them.\n\nI think the spelling might be confusing due to people pronouncing it differently. As I work with lots of British people, I''ve got used to the anglicised pronunciation of Kanban, more like /kʌnbən/, whereas americans, I believe, would pronounce it slightly different, /kænbən/.\nI found an interesting video on youtube explaining the differences in pronunciation and comparison with the Japanese way to say it. I''ve never heard anyone pronouncing it in correct Japanese, though.\n\nhttp://www.youtube.com/watch?v=rGa4JN8c64M\n\n\n\nCheers,\nA', 0, '1', 'Disqus/1.1(2.84):1571910632', '', 0, 0),
(3, 250, 'Tiago Garcia', 'tiagoromerogarcia@gmail.com', 'http://tiagorg.com/', '206.169.185.2', '2014-09-04 22:51:00', '2014-09-04 22:51:00', 'Thanks, Hugo! I really agree with your point. Today we have very handy ways to play with RESTFull APIs, such as Node.js libs like Express, and Ruby libs like Sinatra. I have played with both and I found it very simple to setup effective RESTFull APIs with them. :)', 0, '1', 'Disqus/1.1(2.84):1574559070', '', 1, 0),
(4, 277, 'Summer Kim', 'skim@avenuecode.com', '', '173.247.202.186', '2014-09-15 19:36:00', '2014-09-15 19:36:00', 'Thanks for the post, David! I''d love to visit Scotland sometime in my life.', 0, '1', 'Disqus/1.1(2.84):1590350239', '', 0, 0),
(7, 394, 'Alexandre Paiva', 'ampaiva2060@yahoo.com.br', '', '200.139.147.207', '2014-10-29 21:37:00', '2014-10-29 21:37:00', 'Nice article, friend! I will read the part 2 and post more useful comments! Congrats!', 0, '1', 'Disqus/1.1(2.84):1660070816', '', 0, 0),
(8, 492, 'Alex Miranda', 'alexmirandamoraes@gmail.com', 'http://alexmiranda.net', '187.49.237.214', '2014-10-30 20:01:00', '2014-10-30 20:01:00', 'An enjoyable read and very promising end, well done Renan! Looking forward to the next one :-)', 0, '1', 'Disqus/1.1(2.84):1661755145', '', 0, 0);
